voices.mp3Text: Admiral, but not admirable. Hm hm hm hm.

voices.mp3Text: Ha ha! Blew you off course, did I?

voices.mp3Text: Venomancer, I was never a fan.

voices.mp3Text: That grimoire of his got terrible reviews.
voices.name: Warlock

voices.mp3Text: Pity, Puck. You lightened the air.

voices.mp3Text: I accept this honor on behalf of storms everywhere!
